This product is a derivative work of JMusicBot
(https://github.com/jagrosh/MusicBot).

Copyright 2016-2022 John Grosh (jagrosh) and contributors.

Notable changes in this fork include a browser control panel (Javalin),
optional Discord OAuth for the web UI, play history, LRCLIB lyrics,
Spotify URL resolution (playback via YouTube search), and a patched
SoundCloud client-id tracker for Lavaplayer.

Third-party libraries used by this project include JDA, Lavaplayer,
Javalin, and others named in pom.xml. See each dependency for its
license terms.

